Doc: A limited version of the CDS type used as an underlyer to CDS options in Transparency view, to avoid requiring product type etc.

Source.Contents:
/#
   A limited version of the CDS type used as an underlyer to CDS options in Transparency view, to avoid requiring product type etc.
 #/
record FpML5.transparency.LimitedCreditDefaultSwap {
  # This element contains all the data that appears in the section entitled "1. General Terms" in the 2003 ISDA Credit Derivatives Confirmation.
  generalTerms : FpML5.transparency.GeneralTerms

  # This element contains all the terms relevant to defining the fixed amounts/payments per the applicable ISDA definitions.
  feeLeg : FpML5.transparency.FeeLeg

  # This element contains all the terms relevant to defining the applicable floating rate payer calculation amount, credit events and associated conditions to settlement, and reference obligations.
  protectionTerms : FpML5.transparency.ProtectionTerms

}

generalTerms.Doc: This element contains all the data that appears in the section entitled "1. General Terms" in the 2003 ISDA Credit Derivatives Confirmation.
generalTerms.Name: generalTerms

feeLeg.Doc: This element contains all the terms relevant to defining the fixed amounts/payments per the applicable ISDA definitions.
feeLeg.Name: feeLeg

protectionTerms.Doc: This element contains all the terms relevant to defining the applicable floating rate payer calculation amount, credit events and associated conditions to settlement, and reference obligations.
protectionTerms.Name: protectionTerms
